				\begin{document}$$\left\{ {C_{k} } \right\}_{k = 1}^{n}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M14"><mml:msubsup><mml:mfenced close="}" open="{"><mml:msub><mml:mi>C</mml:mi><mml:mi>k</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:mfenced><mml:mrow><mml:mi>k</mml:mi><mml:mo>=</mml:mo><mml:mn>1</mml:mn></mml:mrow><mml:mi>n</mml:mi></mml:msubsup></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2021_4064_Article_IEq5.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>, where each value is defined as<disp-formula id="Equa"><alternatives><tex-math id="M15">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
